Submission Guidelines
Write clearly and concisely
Show your reasoning, not just the answer
Do not include brute-force dumps without explanation
Focus on analysis, not just tool output
Assume a reviewer will validate your process (we will)
This is not just about getting the flag.
This is about understanding what happened, how it happened, and why it matters.
